title: Jenkins security advisory (AV25-276)
description: On May 14, 2025, Jenkins published a security advisory to address vulnerabilities in the following products:
products: Cadence vManager Plugin  version 4.0.1-286.v9e25a_740b_a_48 and prior
Health Advisor by CloudBees Plugin  version 374.v194b_d4f0c8c8 and prior
OpenID Connect Provider Plugin  version 96.vee8ed882ec4d and prior
WSO2 Oauth Plugin  version 1.0 and prior
solution: Review the references and apply the necessary updates.
